videos.description: Hunter Bryant beats his defender and catches the pass from Jacob Eason to score a touchdown, giving Washington a 14-3 lead over Utah.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Eason connects with Bryant for 34-yard Washington TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eason connects with Bryant for 34-yard Washington TD

videos.description: Jacob Eason's pass is picked off by Utah's Jaylon Johnson and returned 39 yards for a touchdown to cut Washington's lead to 21-19.
videos.headline: Washington's Eason throws pick-6

videos.description: Zack Moss makes the catch and navigates his way to the end zone where he dives to score a nine-yard Utah touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Moss fights for nine-yard Utah TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moss fights for nine-yard Utah TD

videos.description: Tyler Huntley keeps it and narrowly reaches the end zone to score a short one-yard Utah touchdown to give them a 26-21 lead over Washington.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Huntley's TD puts Utah ahead late) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Huntley's TD puts Utah ahead late
